title: dav1d: 1 year later
subtitle: dav1d is a fast AV1 decoder
abstract: dav1d is an open source decoder for the AV1 format, focused on being fast and lean.
description: It was started a bit more than one year ago. This is a talk to see where this project is now, how fast we achieved for decoding AV1 samples and what is left to do on this project.
